Packages 
Package Description
dev.tilegame
Holds the game, launcher and the manager, as well as all the files required to run the game.
dev.tilegame.display
Displays the game window.
dev.tilegame.entities
Entity is User interactive characters.
dev.tilegame.entities.animals
Animals hold the different types of Animals that are available to the user, as well as AI animals.
dev.tilegame.gfx
This file holds all the different animations, the game camera, the sprite sheet, the image loader and the assets.
dev.tilegame.input
File that listens for user key stokes and mouse movements.
dev.tilegame.sound
LoopLoader runs the music on a constant loop.
dev.tilegame.states
States are used to manage stage of the game a user is in.
dev.tilegame.stats  
dev.tilegame.tile
Tile holds all the different tile id's and maps to the images from the text file.
dev.tilegame.tile.bathroom
Holds tile's for the bathroom.
dev.tilegame.tile.bedroom
Holds tile's for the bedroom.
dev.tilegame.tile.decor
Holds different decor tile's.
dev.tilegame.tile.dining
Holds all the tile's for different dinning settings.
dev.tilegame.tile.housing
Holds the tile's for general housing settings.
dev.tilegame.tile.kitchen
Holds the tile's for the kitchen items.
dev.tilegame.tile.livingroom
Holds the tile's for the living room settings.
dev.tilegame.tile.outdoor
Holds the tiles for outdoor world settings.
dev.tilegame.utils
Does basic loading, to load in the text file for the world.
dev.tilegame.worlds
World Generates the game world.
